Describe installed packages

Source: R/get-pkg.R
get_installed_packages.Rd

Displays the name and title of all installed R packages in json format.

Usage

get_installed_packages()

Value

A single string describing installed packages in json.

See Also

  • register_btw_tools() registers this function as a tool for LLMs to call.

  • Other get_*() functions: get_data_frame(), get_environment(), get_installed_packages(), get_package_help(), get_package_vignette(), get_package_vignettes(), get_help_page()
